---
import TerminalWindow from './TerminalWindow.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 border-t border-border">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
      See it in action
    </h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
      A Claude Code session managed through marmy. The agent works, you approve from your phone when it needs you.
    </p>

    <TerminalWindow title="claude — ~/projects/api">
      <div class="space-y-2 text-xs sm:text-sm">
        <div>
          <span class="text-accent">❯</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> claude "add rate limiting to the /api/chat endpoint"</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-text-muted">
          ╭───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
        </div>
        <div class="text-text-muted">
          │ <span class="text-text-primary">Claude Code</span> v1.0.26                                  │
        </div>
        <div class="text-text-muted">
          ╰───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1">
          <span class="text-green">●</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> Reading src/routes/chat.ts...</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-green">●</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> Reading src/middleware/auth.ts...</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-green">●</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> Found existing Express middleware chain</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-2">
          <span class="text-accent">⟡</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> I'll add a sliding-window rate limiter using Redis. Here's my plan:</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pl-4 text-text-muted">
          1. Add <span class="text-accent">express-rate-limit</span> + <span class="text-accent">rate-limit-redis</span> deps
        </div>
        <div class="pl-4 text-text-muted">
          2. Create src/middleware/rateLimit.ts
        </div>
        <div class="pl-4 text-text-muted">
          3. Apply to /api/chat with 60 req/min window
        </div>
        <div class="pl-4 text-text-muted">
          4. Add tests in __tests__/rateLimit.test.ts
        </div>
        <div class="pt-3 border-t border-border mt-2">
          <span class="text-text-muted">marmy →</span>
          <span class="text-green"> ✓ Approved from iPhone</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted"> (2s response time)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1">
          <span class="text-green">●</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> Writing src/middleware/rateLimit.ts...</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-green">●</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> Modifying src/routes/chat.ts...</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-green">●</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> Running npm test... </span>
          <span class="text-green">14 passed</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-2">
          <span class="text-green">✓</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> Done. 3 files changed, 127 lines added.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </TerminalWindow>
  </div>
</section>
